@TheWrathofShane: Did you read the reminder text on [Sundial of the Infinite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sundial of the Infinite)?  

*"and "this turn" and "until end of turn" effects end."*  

When you stop your turn with the Sundial, he will cease to be a creature. Additionally, you can't activate the sundial when the "ability gos on the stack" because that doesn't happen. The effect simply ends when your turn does.
